aa(lp105
VAnother thing is that we had to get rid of all the wax,
p106
aVbecause this was used in the liturgical services
p107
aVof the Greek Orthodox Church
p108
aVand they'd used candle wax.
p109
aVAnd the candle wax was dirty,
p110
aVand we couldn't image through the wax.
p111
aVSo very carefully we had to mechanically scrape off all the wax.
p112
aa(lp113
VIt's hard to tell you exactly
p114
aVhow bad this condition of this book is,
p115
aVbut it came out in little bits very often.
p116
aVAnd normally in a book, you wouldn't worry about the little bits,
p117
aVbut these little bits might contain unique Archimedes text.
p118
aVSo, tiny fragments
p119
aVwe actually managed to put back in the right place.
